{"tid":195627,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"淺田真央宣布引退","createTime":"2017-04-10T17:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T17:25:27.000Z","uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b85ac015f71899b1d692558c6056e408f2d62504","tid":195627,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"日本三屆世錦賽花式滑冰冠軍女神淺田真央，今晚在個人部落格宣布，決定從花式滑冰界引退。消息一出，震驚日本社會，讓很多日本冰迷都覺得非常惋惜。<br />\n26歲的淺田在部落格中表示，她決定引退，是因為去年全日本錦標賽結束後，覺得支撐自己的目標消失了，持續身為選手的力氣沒了，於是決定引退。淺田真央曾奪下2008、2010和2014年世錦賽金牌和2010年冬季奧運銀牌，2014年曾暫時退休一年，但去年日本錦標賽淺田竟只獲得12名，讓她深深受到打擊。<br />\n<br />\n淺田表示，她的花式滑冰人生無悔，（引退）對她來說，這是很大的決定，但卻是她人生中的一個通過點。今後她會找尋新的夢想、目標，會不忘笑容，往前邁進，她真的很感謝至今支持她的人。<br />\n淺田是世界上少數能完成阿克薩爾3周半跳的選手，10幾歲起，在實力與人氣方面一直帶動、支撐著日本的花式滑冰界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170411/1095244/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170411%2F1095244%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=09d1894d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170411/1095244/</a><br />\n<br />\n普皇退役之後到MAO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過退役都算係好事,始終成身傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16013e31ad9b01c7faa44f5aab2b0f04081e350b","tid":195627,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0IyiNbWglQuDyxXi/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0IyiNbWglQuDyxXi%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2456a121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n永遠懷念呢張GIF"},{"pid":"e987fd98cd48374603d342b74794a23acbcd8576","tid":195627,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0IyiNbWglQuDyxXi/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0IyiNbWglQuDyxXi%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2456a121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n永遠懷念呢張GIF</blockquote><br />\n仲有亞古丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc775edcf9670dc5376834cf1c0ad5189410c9e","tid":195627,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f9fca1e1f92bba030e02e669dada8f8c556c84","tid":195627,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}